{
  "stem": "6526.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were working there making-- there was a factory making synthetic rubber, synthetic fuel, and all kinds of other manufacturing, which we did-- which we did work there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And being there-- being there was much, I would say the beginning was much easier because we didn't have that much supervision.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we couldn't run away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when it came to wintertime, it was the end of November, beginning December, when it came to cold weather, there was very little supplies, no heat.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To wash yourself, you had to go outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was water running, sometimes it was frozen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to wash ourself with the snow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if there was-- it was very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we see that we did not make such a good deal running away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then our health was going down, and down, and down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, we got beaten on the-- from very little food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got beaten on the-- on the workplace, where I worked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one time I got beaten up, that my scar-- my-- Your skull.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My skull, my skull was beaten up here in such a way that was blood was running all the time because the blood wasn't red.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The blood was rose, a rose color.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was so thin, that it could never heal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe the blood has a little fat that helps it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because that kapo or the German didn't do right or he saw-- or sometimes we were beaten-- one, one haftling, one prisoner, beat with another.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the SS men want to have some fun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said, go over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did-- does not work with you as you do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hit him because he's not working good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they want me to hit him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How can I hit him?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
